use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 12, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qbf1665702534519.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qbf1665702534519.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qbf1665702534519.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qbf1665702534519\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Load component data from a JSON stream into the specified <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__topic_d125798e1_d125799e1_d125800e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__p_d125801e1_d125802e1_d125803e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentInstance</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">setData</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">JsonStream</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">);</code>\n</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__p_d125804e1_d125805e1_d125806e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">this.setData(vData);</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__section_w530ab1b5b3_w531ab1b5_w532ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1171020e82\">Arguments</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__parml_hht_5jr_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">JsonStream</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">JSON stream containing serialized component information created by\n                     <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getData()</span>.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__section_jb1_sjr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1171020e103\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__section_hqk_sjr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1171020e112\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__p_d125822e1_d125823e1_d125824e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setData()</span> function enables\n            you to load data that has been stored and then retrieved from a local datastore (using\n            the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.datastore</span> APIs), into a component instance. This enables\n            you to load data that has already been downloaded without returning to the server, or to\n            load modified data that was modified while there was no server connection prior to\n            uploading it to the server. It is especially useful in mobile applications.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__example_f5k_1kr_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle exampletitle\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__p_d125825e1_d125826e1_d125827e1\"> Using\n            setData()</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__p_d125828e1_d125829e1_d125830e1\">Assuming the data has been stored in a local\n            database under the <code class=\"ph codeph\">_id</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">songs_dsp</code>, the following code retrieves the data and loads it into the\n            current DSP instance:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104qbf1665702534519_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qbf1665702534519__codeblock_dy5_1kr_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function (vData) {\n uniface.getInstance().setData(vData.title);\n});</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Instance</a><p>The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zom1665702566196.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Disconnected Record Sets</a><p>Disconnected record sets provide a way for components to maintain and share data and its state (such as whether the data has been modified) even when a connection to a database is not available. They are typically used for communication between web components (server pages and web services) and are usually implemented as XML, JSON, or Uniface Structs.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fzt1665702534368.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getData()</a><p>Serialize the component data from the specified component instance into a string with JSON content.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ule1665702755478.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.datastore</a><p>The uniface.datastore API provides access to the local browser-based database used for client-side data storage.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531178\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531178\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "setData() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 12, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Load component data from a JSON stream into the specified uniface.Instance object. ComponentInstance . setData ( JsonStream ); Example: this.setData(vData); Arguments JsonStream JSON stream containing serialized component information created by getData() . Return Value None Description The setData() function enables you to load data that has been stored and then retrieved from a local datastore (using the uniface.datastore APIs), into a component instance. This enables you to load data that has already been downloaded without returning to the server, or to load modified data that was modified while there was no server connection prior to uploading it to the server. It is especially useful in mobile applications. Using setData() Assuming the data has been stored in a local database under the _id songs_dsp , the following code retrieves the data and loads it into the current DSP instance: Explain this code uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function (vData) { uniface.getInstance().setData(vData.title); }); Copy Related Links uniface.Instance The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents. Disconnected Record Sets Disconnected record sets provide a way for components to maintain and share data and its state (such as whether the data has been modified) even when a connection to a database is not available. They are typically used for communication between web components (server pages and web services) and are usually implemented as XML, JSON, or Uniface Structs. getData() Serialize the component data from the specified component instance into a string with JSON content. uniface.datastore The uniface.datastore API provides access to the local browser-based database used for client-side data storage. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}